RawLine: SDM_1103795602,渾沌之初，一支古老氏族於谷內落地生根，因谷內風水環境發展出巫蠱之術，被凡人視為不祥。,浑沌之初，一支古老氏族于谷内落地生根，因谷内风水环境发展出巫蛊之术，被凡人视为不祥。

Items.mt: At the beginning of the chaos, an ancient clan took root in the valley, and was regarded as inauspicious by the mortals because of the feng shui environment in the valley where witchcraft was developed.
